content.rendered:
Directed by Thirumala Kishore.

Written by Thirumala Kishore.

Cast Ram Pothineni(Abhiram / Abhi). Sree Vishnu(Vasudevaiah / Vasu). Lavanya Tripathi(Maggie). Anupama Parameswaran(Maha (as Anupama Parameshwaran)). Priyadarshi Pulikonda(Sathish (as Priyadarshi)) .Mahesh Achanta. Anisha Ambrose(Shreya).Anand. Kaushik Babu(Kaushik). Joy Badlani(Vasu’s relative). Kaumudi(Sishti). Kireeti(Sai (as Kireeti Damaraju)).Raj Madiraju. Komal Pareek(Maggi)

Language Telugu.

Producers Krishna Chaitanya. Ivano Fucci. Ravi Kishore.

Production Sravanthi Cinematics. Goldmines Telefilms. ODU Movies.
